{# Generic platform adapter template.
   Generates a platform-agnostic SKILL.md with only the two required
   frontmatter fields: name and description. No hooks, no metadata,
   no platform-specific configuration.

   The output is packaged as a .skill zip file containing:
   - SKILL.md (this file)
   - scripts/ (if any)
   - references/ (if any)
   - assets/ (if any)

   All script paths must be relative to the skill root directory. #}
---
name: {{ skill_name }}
description: >
  {{ description }}
---

{{ skill_body }}
